:{{DIcon}} How's business?
::'''Lavonne:''' You mean the real estate at the outskirts of the city? Do you remember what I told you once before? "Lady Bronya, our next Supreme Guardian, is gentle and a centrist." Well, turns out that I was right.
::'''Lavonne:''' I told you that the development of areas outside the city was carved in stone. No one had imagined this before, and so property prices were low...
::'''Lavonne:''' But now that the Overworld and Underworld are going to be connected soon, people are going to be buying up property for sure. Naturally, housing prices are going to start climbing up. Then, people can make money hand over fist, right?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} So, did you sell the place?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} So, how much money did you make?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501023986-->
::'''Lavonne:''' Trade secret. No comment. All I can tell you is that real estate has been hot. Better buy while you've got the chance! If you're too late, you might not be able to afford the prices and will be stuck renting a place.
::'''Lavonne:''' In the future, there might be a lot of people looking to live out that way. Demand for housing will outpace supply... I'm revealing insider information I got from some important people in Qlipoth Fort. It is totally reliable!
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Finish: 101150231-->)
:{{DIcon|Exit}} I'm in a hurry. See you later.
::'''Lavonne:''' Smart people always seize opportunities when they present themselves. I trust you are no exception.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
;(Unused &mdash; TalkSentence_301150802)
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301150802-->
